{"questionId":"33290587","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mtext>i</mtext></math>, where <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>v</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℂ</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℝ</mi></math> has roots <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>*</mo></msup></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>*</mo></msup></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>*</mo></msup></math> and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>*</mo></msup></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Determine the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math> and the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mfenced><msup><msub><mi>z</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>*</mo></msup></mfenced><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mfenced><msup><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mn>4</mn></msup></mfenced><mo>*</mo></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>16</mn><mtext>i</mtext></mrow></mfenced><mo>*</mo></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>*</mo><